1 SECTION 6. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
2 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-1154 of Title 63, unless there
3 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
4 A. This act shall not be construed to require a local authority
5 to adopt a program regulating mobile food vendors or to modify its
6 existing program regulating mobile food vendors; provided, the
7 regulations do not conflict with this act.
8 B. This act shall not be construed to impede the State
9 Department of Health or local authority in any investigation of a
10 reported foodborne illness.
